4️⃣ BYPASS RULES

These workflow rules can be bypassed ONLY if user explicitly says:
- "proceed without confirmation"
- "skip documentation check"
- "bypass workflow rules"
- Or similar explicit bypass instruction

Even when bypassed, still provide a follow-up summary for multi-PC sync.

